Revision history for Font-PCF

0.04    2024-08-14
        [CHANGES]
         * Updated for Object::Pad v0.800
         * Swap unit tests from Test::More to Test2::V0
         * Use named parameter support of Sublike::Extended

0.03    2022-04-21
        [CHANGES]
         * More details on printed output of examples/show-glyph

        [BUGFIXES]
         * Quiet the `:experimental(init_expr)` warning of Object::Pad 0.64
         * Fix examples/show-glyph for shift @ARGV

0.02    2022-01-29
        [CHANGES]
         * Use Object::Pad and perl 5.26 signatures
         * Use Syntax::Keyword::Match
         * Drop Struct::Dumb
         * Added a simple example script

0.01    2019-11-09
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
